The evidence with the title 'The Koch Brothers' covert operations | the New Yorker ' says Aug 30, 2010  ... A Republican campaign consultant who has done research on behalf of Charles and David Koch said of the Tea Party , “ the Koch brothers gave the money that founded it . It's like they put the seeds in the ground. Then the rainstorm comes, and the frogs come out of the mud — and they're our candidates!” . 
